1
00:00:22,355 --> 00:00:24,024
I knew they were a thing.

2
00:00:25,325 --> 00:00:25,959
But...

3
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:27,961
is Bingchen going to push my cousin around?

4
00:00:28,695 --> 00:00:29,429
No way.

5
00:00:29,662 --> 00:00:30,597
This is the first time in my life

6
00:00:30,598 --> 00:00:32,465
I've ever seen him so whipped.

7
00:00:33,433 --> 00:00:35,168
You don't know my cousin.

8
00:00:35,468 --> 00:00:36,936
He's way too gullible.

9
00:00:37,704 --> 00:00:38,904
I'm just worried Bingchen will

10
00:00:39,139 --> 00:00:40,439
talk him into

11
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:41,875
giving up everything he's got.

12
00:00:42,842 --> 00:00:43,909
But from what I just saw,

13
00:00:43,910 --> 00:00:45,511
it looked like your cousin

14
00:00:45,512 --> 00:00:47,480
was the one begging for forgiveness.

15
00:00:48,748 --> 00:00:49,215
To be honest,

16
00:00:49,216 --> 00:00:50,483
Xiaoan is actually

17
00:00:51,251 --> 00:00:52,371
pretty cute when he's drunk.

18
00:00:53,553 --> 00:00:54,553
Cute?

19
00:00:55,388 --> 00:00:55,889
I'm standing right here,

20
00:00:55,890 --> 00:00:57,330
and you're calling another guy cute?

21
00:01:03,863 --> 00:01:04,963
Instead of worrying about them,

22
00:01:04,964 --> 00:01:06,565
you should think about
how to make it up to me.

23
00:01:06,566 --> 00:01:07,467
For what?

24
00:01:07,467 --> 00:01:08,201
You posted that embarrassing photo of me

25
00:01:08,202 --> 00:01:09,469
on the fan club page!

26
00:01:11,137 --> 00:01:12,605
Put me down!

27
00:01:13,173 --> 00:01:14,507
It's just fan service.

28
00:01:15,542 --> 00:01:16,976
You can post one of me to get even.

29
00:01:49,676 --> 00:01:50,743
Hei Yan!

30
00:02:48,568 --> 00:02:49,568
Not enough.
